Affiliation = {Suwanna, S; Yuma, S (Corresponding Author), Mahidol Univ, Fac Sci, Dept Phys, Opt \& Quantum Phys Lab, Bangkok 10400, Thailand.
   Kesorn, Aniwat; Talang, Cheewawut Na; Sinsarp, Asawin; Suwanna, Sujin; Yuma, Suraphong, Mahidol Univ, Fac Sci, Dept Phys, Opt \& Quantum Phys Lab, Bangkok 10400, Thailand.
