   Abed Alrhman, Saifeldeen, NYU, Tandon Sch Engn, Dept Chem \& Biomol Engn, New York, NY USA.
   Kirmizialtin, Serdal, New York Univ Abu Dhabi, Ctr Smart Engn Mat, Abu Dhabi 129188, U Arab Emirates.},
