   Adam, Abdullahi Mohamud, Inst BRIAInst, Beaconscope Res Innovat \& AI, Mogadishu, Somalia.
   Yusuf, Abdinasir Mohamed; Arab, Omar Abdi, Inst Engineers Somalia, Mogadishu, Somalia.
   Yusuf, Abdinasir Mohamed; Arab, Omar Abdi, Somali Consulting \& Engn Serv, Mogadishu, Somalia.
