   Espinal-jimenez, A., Univ Guanajuato, Dept Estudios Org, Guanajuato 36250, Mexico.
   Camacho-lopez, S., Ctr Invest Cient \& Educ Super Ensenada, Dept Opt, Carretera Ensenada Tijuana 3918,Zona Playitas, Tijuana 22860, Baja California, Mexico.
   Garcia-granada, A. A.; Rostro-gonzalez, H., Univ Ramon Llull, Sch Engn IQS, Via Augusta 390, Barcelona 08017, Spain.},
DOI = {10.1364/AO.530032},
Keywords-Plus = {OXIDES},
